      <title>阿根廷考虑多年忽视后的输电线招标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/argentina-mulls-tender-for-power-lines-after-years-of-neglect</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷正在紧急制定一项“市场解决方案”来建设其国家高压输电线网络，这是电网中一个被严重忽视的部分，长期以来限制了电力生产的增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/argentina-mulls-tender-for-power-lines-after-years-of-neglect</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 18:56:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>使用贝莱德代币作为抵押品越来越成为主流</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/use-of-blackrock-tokens-as-collateral-moves-closer-to-mainstream</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着一批金融公司投票通过代币化股票的使用准则，允许使用贝莱德和富兰克林邓普顿等主流华尔街巨头的货币市场基金代币化股票作为交易抵押品的努力取得了重大进展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/use-of-blackrock-tokens-as-collateral-moves-closer-to-mainstream</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 18:55:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>TotalEnergies 称英国石油税将损害投资和运营</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/totalenergies-says-uk-oil-tax-will-hurt-investment-operations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[首席执行官帕特里克·普亚内 (Patrick Pouyanne) 表示，英国计划中的石油和天然气税变化将促使道达尔能源公司 (TotalEnergies SE) 减少资本支出并重组该国的业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/totalenergies-says-uk-oil-tax-will-hurt-investment-operations</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 18:08:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>改革生效后货币市场基金依然风靡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/money-market-funds-stay-in-vogue-even-as-reforms-go-into-effect</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管监管改革对该行业征收了昂贵的强制性费用，货币市场基金仍然吸引了创纪录数量的现金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/money-market-funds-stay-in-vogue-even-as-reforms-go-into-effect</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 17:54:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Diamond 明年将停止棒球转播，且不签订新协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/diamond-to-drop-baseball-broadcasts-next-year-without-new-deals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[律师周三在法庭上表示，除非俱乐部老板与这家破产的广播公司达成新的版权协议，否则钻石体育集团明年将停止转播除一支美国职业棒球大联盟球队以外的所有球队的比赛。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/diamond-to-drop-baseball-broadcasts-next-year-without-new-deals</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 17:39:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行 10 月降息势头似乎不可阻挡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/ecb-momentum-for-an-october-rate-cut-is-looking-unstoppable</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在三周前，欧洲央行官员还认为降息不太可能，但现在看来，当他们于 10 月 17 日再次确定借贷成本时，降息几乎已成定局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/ecb-momentum-for-an-october-rate-cut-is-looking-unstoppable</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 09:16:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>油价缩减涨幅，因有迹象显示市场能够消化中东动荡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-2</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价回吐涨幅，因数据显示美国原油库存不断增加，进一步证明市场供应充足，能够吸收来自中东的潜在干扰。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-2</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 22:51:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
